WeNow: your digital eco-driving coach

Improve your energy efficiency and offset your CO[2] emissions

   Play Video

Train your drivers in eco-driving with WeNow

   WeNow’s connected solution for cars will help you save fuel through an
   energy efficiency management tool and eco-driving –and reduce your
   impact on the climate. With WeNow, you can track the energy performance
   of your business motor fleet, cut your fuel consumption by 5 to 15% and
   offset your CO[2] emissions.

   Télécharger sur l'App Store Télécharger sur Google Play

Connecting
your fleet

   The WeNowBox is a device that only takes 5 minutes to set up in your
   car. It provides a real-time assessment of the car’s performance in
   order to identify its fuel waste factors. The WeNowBox collects some of
   the car’s data –consumption, cost of rides, mileage, time spent in the
   car, CO[2] emissions – and compares them with the fuel cards and
   consumption of similar cars in WeNow’s database.

Eco-driving your way
towards energy efficiency

   Why train your drivers in eco-driving? Driving in a smoother and more
   conscious manner helps you reduce both your fuel consumption and CO[2]
   emissions. WeNow coaches your drivers in eco-driving through a
   dedicated mobile app tailored to your needs and monthly reports on
   their performances. On the online platform dedicated to your fleet, you
   can also organize challenges and boost your community of drivers to
   keep them motivated!

Go
carbon-neutral

   WeNow is the first company that allows you to automatically measure
   your fleet’s carbon balance and offset all your gas emissions! By
   supporting certified projects around the world that meet the highest
   international standards and aim to cut the same amount of CO[2] as the
   amount emitted by your fleet, your driving can go 100% carbon-neutral.

   [no_gps-2.png]

   To make it easier to adopt by your drivers, WeNow does not use GPS to
   track and locate your vehicles. All the data is collected and processed
   on a dedicated online platform: you’ll know everything about the energy
   efficiency of your connected fleet! And if you already have an on-board
   device in your vehicles, you’ll just have to connect WeNow to your
   system to benefit from WeNow’s energy efficiency analysis of your
   fleet, eco-driving training for your drivers and carbon-neutral
   solutions.

   “Our organization is very committed to sustainable development, so it’s
   always been really important for us to choose the least polluting
   vehicles. But we were missing one thing: training the people that drive
   our vehicles. WeNow helps us sensitize all our drivers in a fun way, to
   help us further reduce our consumption and CO[2] emissions.”
   — Yannick
   — YannickMotor fleet manager

   “What we liked about WeNow is that it helps you both save fuel and
   offset your gas emissions. That’s a real innovation.”
   — Brigitte
