   “I’ve always tried to pollute as little as possible with my cars. I’ve
   had a very positive experience with WeNow. For my three latest trips
   from Paris to the south of France, in the same conditions and taking
   the same route, my fuel consumption drastically fell! From 6.4
   litres/100km to 5.6 litres/100km and now 5.1L litres/100km, I’ve saved
