WeNow helps you
manage your fleet

Reduce fuel consumption and maximize the energy efficiency of your fleet

   WeNow helps you manage your fleet with an online dashboard that
   displays your vehicles’ performance indicators. You can now maximize
   your fleet’s energy efficiency by comparing your cars to similar
   vehicles in WeNow’s database, in terms of fuel consumption (shown by
   fuel cards) and potential fuel savings by each driver.
   Request a quote!

WeNow for individual customers

   The WeNowBox is also available for individual drivers! Fitting your car
   with WeNow’s connected box will help you track your fuel consumption,
   change some of your driving habits and make your rides more
   energy-efficient, without making them longer. And the best part is that
   offsetting your gas emissions will cost you less than what you’ll save
   in fuel consumption. Choose our innovative solution and drive neutral!

   Télécharger sur l'App Store Télécharger sur Google Play

   With WeNow, you help deliver a fun eco-driving training to new drivers:
   they can share their performances with the community and set each other
   challenges. Each time they improve their driving or energy efficiency,
   they can win points and get rewards. Protecting our planet can actually
   be easy and fun!

Offset your CO[2] emissions
and manage your carbon tax

Achieve a neutral carbon footprint with WeNow

   WeNow is the first customized eco-driving coaching solution that also
   helps you achieve a neutral carbon footprint. Our WeNowBox helps you
   measure, reduce and offset your CO[2] emissions!

Offset your CO[2] emissions… at a neutral cost!

   It is extremely difficult to totally cut your carbon emissions when you
   travel, even if you drive an electric or hybrid car –both are powered
   by electricity, which in itself is hardly ever neutral in terms of
   CO[2]emissions. However, you can offset your gas emissions by
   supporting a project that will capture the same amount of carbon
   somewhere in the world. That way, you can achieve a neutral carbon
   footprint.

   WeNow’s original offer is to help you make fuel savings and give you
   the opportunity to use part of these savings to support carbon-neutral
   projects. So not only will your business fleet drive neutral, but on
   top of that you’ll be saving money.

Carbon-neutral projects

   You can achieve a neutral carbon footprint by contributing financially
   to voluntary offsetting projects that will reduce CO[2] emissions:
   planting trees (that capture CO[2]), cutting sources of CO[2] or
   improving the energy performance of certain systems in order to reduce
   their CO[2] emissions.  Find out what projects you can support!

Take control over your carbon taxes!

   Carbon taxes on fuel and business vehicles will continue to grow in the
   years to come. WeNow helps you anticipate regulations related to carbon
   taxes and reduce your gas emissions by monitoring your business fleets’
   performance indicators on a dedicated dashboard. Anticipate the
   purchase of vehicles tailored to your driving needs, train your drivers
   in eco-driving and offset your carbon emissions! You can also promote
   your fleet’s carbon neutrality to your clients, staff and non-financial
   rating agencies.

